{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because from 1948 till 1956, the Hungarian soccer was ten miles above every other footballing nation in the world That includes England, Brazil, Uruguay, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had a 10-year period of soccer-- and I'm not public relationing for it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But it has a 10 years where you could find a world-class footballer in every corner in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you could buy them for sixpence a dozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's how it was, the standard in football.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So those days, to play first-division soccer in Hungary was a tremendously big achievement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I went for a trial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I became a member of a team which belonged to a huge textile factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the Hungarian sports those days were communist, which meant that, on paper, you were not professional.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "On real life, you were professional.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You were more professional than a professional, because you had such a power as a well-known footballer that, if your friend was in jail, you could go and get him out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Professional players in the west couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They give you a job, like you became a time analyst without knowing how to add up two and two.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But that was the only way they could pay you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So the Hungarian sport could appear on every Olympic games where professional athletes was competing with amateurs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And our status in the world sport was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, gold medals in Olympic games in Hungary-- even in 1936 in Berlin, they had 10 gold medals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they run third in the world among the nation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And from then on-- in Helsinki '14, in London '16, and whatever it is, and even in Melbourne when only a skeleton staff came, they collected quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became a professional footballer.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
